title: Day 5 - The Tunnel
itunes:title: Day 5 - The Tunnel
itunes:subtitle: The Bad Days
description:
The Bad Days, Day 5: Every school has its rumors, its gossip, its scary stories. Students say the words, tell the tales, but few ever take the time to actually investigate and see for themselves. Maybe there's a reason for that...
